Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun from the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What.. what is this? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock high! Five ancient Simoun, closing in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:22.71,Titles,,0,0,0,,Sortie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Four o'clock level! Aircraft silhouettes sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Confirm that, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They appear to be Argentine cruise missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura, you take a Simile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard the enemy Simoun are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll destroy the missiles headed for the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the Highlands' Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:45.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} and the {\i1}Messis{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will have to deal with them on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:48.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:49.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, we need to do what we can, with all our might!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock low!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:22.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,More aeroplane silhouettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Identify them! How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Argentine cruise missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Number: twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock low, more missiles incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:45.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether we perform Ri Maajons to send off the souls of the dead, or to drive away the enemy, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,it doesn't change the fact that we're performing Ri Maajons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what I {\i1}used{\i0} to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:24.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:25.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, the shrapnel is going to fall on the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I don't believe that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Maajons are the same,\Nbut their meaning is totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, she...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon, how about you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, what about the enemy Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,They seem to have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:38.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're turning around and flying away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy's Highland Simoun will soon be out of visual range, sir!  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the enemy Simoun attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they had attacked us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we would have been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your quarters, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:10.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Defence Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simile which was carrying Sibylla Mamiina's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has not returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was almost certainly intercepted by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying, but the incident took place within our Holy Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,We no longer have control of our own airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What of Sibylla Mamiina's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:01.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, we have no time for such trivial matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The situation is already—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:05.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you just say that Sibylla Mamiina's body is a trivial matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister, did I really just hear you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:08.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are not to inform the sibyllae of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the Simoun among the Argentine forces today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:25.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a show of force, to prove to us that they can attack whenever they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that really is what they're capable of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:49.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that this could have happened while we were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There has to be something we can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is your wound, Sibylla Morinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:15.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif, do you know how to wrap a bandage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, Rodoreamon's lack of skill is shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, allow me, Sibylla Rodoreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The flight surgeon was busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:31.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The doc's at the Grand Temple, tending to the people who were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave her in your capable hands, Wapourif!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:39.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are still a lot of things that we'll have to do, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... I like the Ri Maajons that we offer to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you know, I think everyone else feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's the damage to the Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe that we will only need to replace the canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, we just finished repairing the Sibylla Aurea's Simoun, and now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:22.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it was the only thing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you please take better care of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will ask you once more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:06.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do we really have no way to repel the combined forces of the Highlands and the Archipelago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,At such a critical time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:16.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you{\i0} were the one responsible for carrying off three of our Simoun sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that we are well past the time for recriminations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:24.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let us return to the object of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,One hour ago, the Highlands and Archipelago proposed a ceasefire between their alliance and our Simulacrum Theocracy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:39.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think they are suing for peace,\Nwhen they have the power to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:43.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you haven't forgotten the Highlanders' previous method of "negotiating" a peace agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the people are voicing their desire for an end to this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that these "proposals" of theirs are just lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we had opened peace talks earlier, we would have—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}sick{\i0} of hearing about your grudges against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how you think of yourself, you are a Simoun sibylla. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know about anything but fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she was a fighter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:28.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,But her prayers blessed many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people looked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses will protect us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses will defeat all the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right... so you must be patient, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I didn't think you would be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:15.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Aaeru are blessing the people below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that Aaeru's participating, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would have expected you to be the first to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think she belongs by your side, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand why,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,but I feel that you should have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:05.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:12.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, would you take care of Mamiina for me from now on? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought that you would keep something secret from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:39.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand what you want any more! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I want, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guys, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! It seems that they're pushing for another peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard about it from Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this information reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Were you the one who told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only a handful of people know of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I decided that you deserved to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will the war really end this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:36.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Angulas came to us pretending to be a translator for the peace conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... maybe this time it's for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:45.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is possible that you will all be able to leave the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. There's nothing we can really do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:57.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can only do... what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, about our operational plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, Paraietta said the very same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and we'll help with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,To guard against incursions from the mountain sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to send out rotating patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand we're in the middle of a crisis, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} is so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}, a ship of the same class, has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's shocking. Almost unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's almost as hard to believe as you and Guragief fighting with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:48.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're aware of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:54.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You both have strong feelings... that you're unwilling to concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief is... too earnest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, he sure can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that you both decided to be men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:10.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should patch things up with Guragief as quickly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,You never know when your time will be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why are they attacking us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:31.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like they say, "they won't quit until we make them."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cast off the moonrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Casting off the moonrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Up ship! Climb at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ascending at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Situation report!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock high! Five ancient Simoun approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eleven o'clock level, several Argentine medium fighters! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready the Simoun for immediate takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are the priestesses from Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not here yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Anubituf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Order Chor Tempest to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy is almost upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:41.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Send word for the sibyllae to stand by on the port flight deck. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll give their orders to them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, I need to ask you to take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} will be the second wave of our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to direct our offensive from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:59.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until the Captain returns, I have the conn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? Go! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our orders are to stand by on the port flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:11.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn that Anubituf! What is that sly bastard plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That geezer is so freakin' annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing by at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:18.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait, Sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though it may not look like it,\NI used to be a sibylla, just like all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you're going to fly a Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:38.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. We have only five Simoun with which to intercept the enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:43.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I shall fly a Simile, and issue orders directly to you all from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will need you to follow those orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:45.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:52.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas, how is your wound? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's been very carefully treated. Everything is fine, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:56.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,G-Get a Simile ready, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:00.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, a word if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have dragged you into this war... and that must come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:32.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I very much regret that we have not been able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain Anubituf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I shall never forget your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, you guys don't need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We already decided, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we can do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we will do with all our might!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are drastically outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:58.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,We shall pull them towards us as much as we can, dive rapidly, and then hit them hard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The course of the battle will be decided by this first attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,All batteries, fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, suckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We showed those losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two of you, watch your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:32.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Y-You heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course not! We were just talking about you two, and figured that you were probably saying something filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:37.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, do tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably another inane comment from Floe, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's likely, isn't it, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't say anything like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is Chor Tempest always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alti's the one who always—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Floe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Captain's Simile, approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:40.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite Chor Tempest's actions, Central Command concluded that the war was a lost cause... 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:49.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and accepted the peace treaty offered by Plumbum and Argentum a few days later. 
